metadata.name: Mar-A-Lago 1
metadata.description:
This song and visual was written, engineered, produced, filmed and edited entirely by Me. 

Mar-A-Lago isn't just the infamous Donald Trump resort that was raided by the Feds. The term itself in Spanish Translates to "Sea-to-Lake". That describes my current journey in music completely. I have been involved in the Music industry for some time and it feels like a giant stormy sea. You witness both small and huge waves come and go, its filled with money hungry sharks, and its a constant battle to stay afloat. I've come to realize that being on a more independent journey (especially in Web 3) has been much more fulfilling for me. Similar to a lake, its been much calmer and enjoyable. Its easier to navigate and allows for more intimate connections. Everybody wont understand your journey, but the journey is YOURS..... Alone on this ride I go.


Within this video are 2 NFTS that I have sent to all my prior collectors, and 1 that I will send to collectors of this piece. The NFT'S are alternate pieces of cover art, created by myself with the help of AI.
